2.1. Communicator
Communicates with Remote System.
Communicator is a class taking full responsibility to network communication with remote system. You can register a Provider, an object would be provided to remote system, thorugh this Communicator. Also, DriverController>, who can use remote system's Provider, is created by this Communicator.

Communicator.getDriver

In addition, Communicator is the top-level abstract class. All the classes responsible for network communication in TGrid inherit this Communicator class. If you want to know more, go to the 3. Protocols chapter.


    Server
    Client




